; padding: 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-style: dotted; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span class=\"_0000FF\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255) !important;\"><b>贵阳 &ldquo;二七路&rdquo;、兴关路小吃一条街：感受 &ldquo;舌尖上的贵州&rdquo;，了解贵州地道美食，如烤鱼、丝娃娃、肠旺面、牛肉粉、豆腐圆子等小吃；</b></span></div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photos\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo detail-journey-photo-2\" style=\"margin: 0px -10px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none; width: 350px; height: 225px;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/10/AB/Cii9EFdfwuaIUPFrAAIT7rfSSbIAAGikgOlq1AAAhQG338_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/10/AB/Cii9EFdfwuaIUPFrAAIT7rfSSbIAAGikgOlq1AAAhQG338_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"丝娃娃\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 350px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none; width: 350px; height: 225px;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/10/AD/Cii9EVdfwwaIFlv9AAK-AVQ_BlEAAGikwEZRvEAAr4Z690_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/10/AD/Cii9EVdfwwaIFlv9AAK-AVQ_BlEAAGikwEZRvEAAr4Z690_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"酸汤鱼\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 350px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-feature-photo-sep\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-style: dotted; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\">餐饮</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-list\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">早餐：敬请自理 午餐：敬请自理 晚餐：敬请自理</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-style: dotted; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\">住宿</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-list\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">贵阳华桥酒店 创客酒店 景轩阁酒店 贝斯特酒店或其它备选酒店</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-style: dotted; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"J_JourneyDay2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-head\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; position: relative; line-height: 26px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold;\"><span class=\"icon detail-journey-day\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -57px; top: -5px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 36px; font-size: 16px; background-image: url(&quot;/static/img/201611/modules/tour/tour/icons-s03a8f95e63.png&quot;); background-position: -126px -480px; background-repeat: no-repeat; overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; height: 47px; width: 40px;\">D2</span>贵阳黄果树瀑布贵阳</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-seprate-solid\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\">行程描述</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-style: dotted; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">早餐后，乘旅游巴士（车程约 2.5 小时）赴<span class=\"_0000FF\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255) !important;\">【黄果树瀑布风景区】</span>，黄果树瀑布是中国第一大瀑布，也是亚洲最大的瀑布。黄果树瀑布是这些瀑布群中最壮美的一个，它高 77.8 米、宽 101 米；瀑布犹如万缕银丝披挂、轻柔多姿。【水帘洞】位于黄果树瀑布四十米至四十七米的高度上，全长一百三十四米，共有六个洞窗、五个洞厅、三股洞泉和六个通道。随后前往<span class=\"_0000FF\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255) !important;\">【天星桥风景区】</span>，此处号称 &ldquo;有水皆成瀑、是石总盘根景区是由地下河塌陷形成，阳光这下，闪闪发光。游览黄果树景区内最宽的瀑布<span class=\"_0000FF\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255) !important;\">【陡坡塘瀑布】</span>，又称 &ldquo;<span class=\"_0000FF\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255) !important;\">吼瀑</span>&rdquo;，是黄果树瀑布群中瀑顶最宽的瀑布，是《西游记》拍摄地。<br />\r\n晚餐后欣赏贵州大型民族歌舞表演&mdash;&mdash;<span class=\"_0000FF\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255) !important;\">《多彩贵州风》</span>（需要自费：248 元 / 人）以原生态的少数民族文化和舞蹈全新整合再现，充分和全景的展现贵州浓郁的少数民族风情风貌，与《印象刘三姐》《云南映象》并称为 &ldquo;西南三部曲&rdquo;，是游客到贵州休闲度假期间不可不看的一场文化饕餮盛宴。</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photos\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo detail-journey-photo-4\" style=\"margin: 0px -10px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none; width: 350px; height: 225px;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/DC/13/Cii9EFdD_3CIOGzfAAA9BwJmYFAAAGJlwHW9YYAAD0f79_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpeg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/DC/13/Cii9EFdD_3CIOGzfAAA9BwJmYFAAAGJlwHW9YYAAD0f79_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpeg\" alt=\"除了雄伟的黄果树瀑布\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 350px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none; width: 350px; height: 225px;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/DC/13/Cii9EVdD_3GICduOAABjy5L4hZ4AAGJlwHXMqUAAGPj39_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpeg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/DC/13/Cii9EVdD_3GICduOAABjy5L4hZ4AAGJlwHXMqUAAGPj39_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpeg\" alt=\"还有壮阔的陡坡塘瀑布&lt;br/&gt;\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 350px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-feature-photo-sep\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: l