\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">早餐后乘车前往游览<span class=\"_FF0000\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0) !important;\">【布达拉宫景区】（门票 100 元 / 人，费用已含，游览时间约 1.5 小时）</span>，布达拉宫位于中国西藏自治区首府拉萨市区西北的玛布日山上，是一座宫堡式建筑群，是松赞干布为迎娶尺尊公主和文成公主而兴建。依次参观西日光殿、东日光殿、强巴佛殿（强康）、坛城殿（鲁朗康）、殊胜三界殿（萨松朗杰）、长寿乐集殿（其美丹吉）、十三世达赖喇嘛灵塔殿、上师殿（喇嘛拉康）、七世达赖喇嘛灵塔殿、圣观音殿（帕巴拉康）、八世达赖喇嘛灵塔殿、九世达赖喇嘛灵塔、时轮坛城殿（堆廓拉康、释迦能仁殿（土旺拉康）、无量寿佛殿（次巴拉康）、法王洞（曲结竹秋）、普贤追随殿（公桑中珠康）、响铜殿（利马拉康）、红宫二回廓（壁画）、西有寂圆满大殿（措庆努西平措）、菩提道次第殿（朗仁拉康）、持明殿（仁僧拉康）、五世达赖喇嘛灵塔殿（色东康）、世袭殿（冲热拉康）。</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photos\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo detail-journey-photo-4\" style=\"margin: 0px -10px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none; width: 350px; height: 225px;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com//filebroker/cdn/snc/4d/5f/4d5f229ecc3ffb4004f2f8fe3145e200_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com//filebroker/cdn/snc/4d/5f/4d5f229ecc3ffb4004f2f8fe3145e200_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"布达拉宫\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 350px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none; width: 350px; height: 225px;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com//filebroker/cdn/snc/0a/58/0a5883eb96faa1a65277109b032942f7_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com//filebroker/cdn/snc/0a/58/0a5883eb96faa1a65277109b032942f7_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"布达拉宫\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 350px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-feature-photo-sep\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none; width: 350px; height: 225px;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com//filebroker/cdn/snc/f7/b5/f7b58da3c2aa6a33badcfc77328328c5_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com//filebroker/cdn/snc/f7/b5/f7b58da3c2aa6a33badcfc77328328c5_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"布达拉宫\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 350px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none; width: 350px; height: 225px;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com//filebroker/cdn/snc/39/5c/395c53a56a1c7ad9e9658ba4c5e27a51_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com//filebroker/cdn/snc/39/5c/395c53a56a1c7ad9e9658ba4c5e27a51_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"布达拉宫\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 350px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-feature-photo-sep\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\">温馨提示</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">☆宫殿较高，上下要慢行。殿内比较阴冷，即使夏季也准备件外套。布达拉宫不允许导游在景区内讲解，只能在外面讲解完。<span class=\"_FF0000\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0) !important;\">【布达拉宫严禁拍照，请游客进入前一定不要带相机、摄像机、带拍照功能的手机。每年都有不遵守布宫规定而引起不愉快的事件发生，请各位游客文明出行，遵守文物保护单位的规定】</span><br />\r\n☆布达拉宫里面非常难找厕所，如果着急最好在参观前解决。<br />\r\n☆布达拉宫建筑古老，通道狭窄并有许多木质楼梯，金顶群是布达拉宫承重的地方，加之上下共用一个狭窄的楼梯，接纳过多游客容易造成安全隐患，所以参观完了就尽就尽快离开，请游客参观和上下楼梯时一定按秩序行走，注意安全，不要拥挤。</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">午餐后参观<span class=\"_FF0000\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0) !important;\">【大昭寺】（门票 85 元 / 人，费用已含，游览时间约 1 小时）</span>依次参观囊廓，沿千佛廊绕 &ldquo;觉康&rdquo; 佛殿转一圈 &ldquo;囊廓&rdquo; 方为圆满。唐蕃会盟碑进入大昭寺前面的小广场，首先映入眼帘的是被围墙围起的两块石碑。南边一块便是著名的唐蕃会盟碑，唐长庆三年 (823 年) 用藏汉两种文字刻写。碑的旁边有一棵柳树，据传由文成公主亲手种植，当地人称为公主柳。</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photos\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo detail-journey-photo-4\" style=\"margin: 0px -10px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none; width: 350px; height: 225px;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com//filebroker/cdn/snc/ea/44/ea445fe9229f173db1d5b828b180663d_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com//filebroker/cdn/snc/ea/44/ea445fe9229f173db1d5b828b180663d_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"大昭寺\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 350px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none; width: 350px; height: 225px;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com//filebroker/cdn/snc/06/ad/06adb6dc0a2c414d76487fbbf8485fd4_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com//filebroker/cdn/snc/06/ad/06adb6dc0a2c414d76487fbbf8485fd4_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"大昭寺\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 350px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-feature-photo-sep\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none; width: 350px; height: 225px;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com//filebroker/cdn/snc/e6/d0/e6d08abec5affa3bc9f864f85ba20b56_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com//filebroker/cdn/snc/e6/d0/e6d08abec5affa3bc9f864f85ba20b56_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"大昭寺\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 350px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none; width: 350px; height: 225px;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com//filebroker/cdn/snc/b0/58/b058afc1c57ae908f4492042403daaad_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com//filebroker/cdn/snc/b0/58/b058afc1c57ae908f4492042403daaad_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"大昭寺\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 350px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-feature-photo-sep\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\">温馨提示</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">☆西藏土木结构建筑，融合藏、唐、尼泊尔、印度建筑风格，也是仅存的最大的吐蕃王朝建筑；<br />\r\n☆佛祖 12 岁等身像，世界上仅存 3 尊佛祖等身像，唯二在拉萨其中 8 岁等身像供奉在拉萨小昭寺但 12 岁等身像为鎏金铜像精美与尊贵。<br />\r\n☆朝圣路的终点，门前的青石地板上有留下了等身长头的很深印痕。<br />\r\n☆可观看或参与朝圣者转经，主要是以寺为中心分为内圈、中圈和外圈。☆藏传佛教中 &ldquo;格西&rdquo;（藏传佛教中的高级学位，相当于博士）的产地。☆大昭寺金顶观赏【布达拉宫远景】亦可俯视大昭寺广场。<br />\r\n☆拉萨转经筒最多的寺庙，可按顺时针边走边推动转经筒。<br />\r\n☆寺内的壁画精美绝伦可以很好的了解整个建寺历史。</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">之后前往<span class=\"_FF0000\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0) !important;\">【八廓街手工艺品市场】（无门票，自由活动时间约 60 分钟）</span>，感受西藏的人文风土，浏览民族特色和异域风情的手工制品，游览完毕入住酒店休息。<br />\r\n<span class=\"_FF0000\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0) !important;\">八角街是藏族人购物的主要地区，商店林立，货品良莠不齐，游客购物一定要谨慎，以免引起不必要的麻烦。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photos\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo detail-journey-photo-4\" style=\"margin: 0px -10px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none; width: 350px; height: 225px;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com//filebroker/cdn/snc/6a/2a/6a2aeba6193087effcccf71b4a6a0150_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com//filebroker/cdn/snc/6a/2a/6a2aeba6193087effcccf71b4a6a0150_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"八角街\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 350px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none; width: 350px; height: 225px;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com//filebroker/cdn/snc/c5/6c/c56cc7d73da1b148c1e6bb7d3745ad00_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com//filebroker/cdn/snc/c5/6c/c56cc7d73da1b148c1e6bb7d3745ad00_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"八角街\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 350px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-feature-photo-sep\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"