 color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span class=\"_FF0000\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0) !important;\">此线路为散客拼团行程，在晚上 22：00 之前会有第二天出团导游跟您电话联系确认第二天的行程及出游时间，请您保持手机畅通</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-style: dotted; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\">餐饮</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-list\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">早餐：含 午餐：含 晚餐：含</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-style: dotted; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\">住宿</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-list\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">太阳岛大酒店、嘎吉林大酒店、雅鲁藏布、四川宾馆</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-style: dotted; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"J_JourneyDay3\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-head\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; position: relative; line-height: 26px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold;\"><span class=\"icon detail-journey-day\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -57px; top: -5px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 36px; font-size: 16px; background-image: url(&quot;/static/img/201611/modules/tour/tour/icons-s03a8f95e63.png&quot;); background-position: -126px -480px; background-repeat: no-repeat; overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; height: 47px; width: 40px;\">D3</span>拉萨羊卓雍错卡若拉冰川日喀则（最高海拔 5560 米）</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-seprate-solid\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\">行程描述</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-style: dotted; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">早餐后约 07：30 乘车沿 318 国道，翻越岗巴拉雪山（海拔 4900 米）前往羊卓雍湖（车程 120 公里，约 3 小时车程）。抵达后游览<span class=\"_FF0000\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0) !important;\">【羊卓雍湖】（门票 40 元 / 人，费用已含。游览时间约 1 小时）</span>羊卓雍湖藏语意为 &ldquo;碧玉湖&rdquo; 是西藏三大圣湖之一，位雅鲁藏布江南岸、山南浪卡子县境内。羊湖岔口较多，像珊瑚枝一般，因此它在藏语中又被称为 &ldquo;上面的珊瑚湖&rdquo;。羊卓雍错湖光山色，景色如画，仿如置身人间仙境，羊湖是集高原湖泊、雪山、岛屿、牧场、温泉、寺庙等多种景观为一体的、独特的自然风景区，周围还有常年不溶的雪山冰峰。湖泊、雪峰与蓝天融为一体，让人流连忘返。</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\">注意事项</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span class=\"_FF0000\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0) !important;\">冈巴拉山上很多可以提供牦牛拍照，请先讲好价格，以免造成不必要麻烦。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\">羊卓雍措</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">羊卓雍错通常简称为 &ldquo;羊湖&rdquo;，与玛旁雍错、纳木错并称西藏三大神湖。羊卓雍错的水源来自四周念青唐古拉山脉的雪水，没有出水口，雪水的流入与自然的蒸发达到一种奇特的动态平衡，湖水随着光线变幻，演化成千变万化的蓝色。这里藏南最大的水鸟栖息地，每逢冬季群鸟南徙至此，在湖岸及湖心岛一带，天鹅、水鸽、黄鸭、鱼鹰以及斑头雁都非常地多并且羊卓雍错是寻找转世灵童的圣湖，大活佛可以从湖中看出显影，指示灵童所在的大方位。不同时刻阳光的照射，羊湖会显现出不同层次、极其丰富的蓝色，如梦似幻，初见羊湖，她的艳丽让人几乎不敢相信。游览亮点：☆西藏三大圣湖之一，水源为唐古拉雪水，湖水根据阳光的照射呈现出不同的蓝色。☆冬季时大批候鸟栖息在湖岸及湖心岛一带，为藏南最大的水鸟栖息地。☆虔诚的佛教徒认为每年都要绕湖一圈，这等于他们到拉萨朝圣一次，可见其地位。☆藏民心中的圣湖因为大活佛可以从湖中看出转世灵童的方位。</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photos\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo detail-journey-photo-4\" style=\"margin: 0px -10px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none; width: 350px; height: 225px;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com//filebroker/cdn/snc/f3/64/f3648eba491b5743840f414872a9df02_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com//filebroker/cdn/snc/f3/64/f3648eba491b5743840f414872a9df02_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"羊卓雍措\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 350px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journ