/span>该寺修建于 1447 年的黄教六大寺之一、历代班禅额尔德尼驻锡地&mdash;扎什伦布寺，远眺整个寺院依山坡而筑，背附高山，殿宇毗连，群楼叠叠，金顶红墙的高在主建筑群雄伟、浑厚、壮观、金碧辉煌。寺内香炉紫烟升腾供台灯火闪烁，众佛尊容各异。大殿里僧侣诵经井然；佛像前，信徒顶礼膜拜。五百多年来它强烈地吸引着国内外佛教信徒。游人在这里朝拜、观瞻。寺内供奉有高 26 米的室内铜像&mdash;强巴佛。瞻仰十世班禅大师灵塔后游览日喀则自由市场。</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\">扎什伦布寺</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">扎什伦布寺金顶红墙，重楼叠宇，高低错落，被誉为后藏至尊。黄教六大名寺之一，藏传佛教格鲁派在后藏地区的寺庙，班禅大师的驻锡地，也是历代班禅举行宗教和政治活动的主要场所，与拉萨三大寺并称为西藏四大寺。寺内有强巴佛镀金铜像，慈善端祥，雍容大度，造型生动。</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photos\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo detail-journey-photo-2\" style=\"margin: 0px -10px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none; width: 350px; height: 225px;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com//filebroker/cdn/snc/c5/da/c5da3c20fb87b00cc126a449224b00ea_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com//filebroker/cdn/snc/c5/da/c5da3c20fb87b00cc126a449224b00ea_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"扎什伦布寺\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 350px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none; width: 350px; height: 225px;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com//filebroker/cdn/online/26/2e/262ef5ce_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com//filebroker/cdn/online/26/2e/262ef5ce_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"扎什伦布寺\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 350px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-feature