ass=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\">景点介绍；灵山大佛</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\">自费【灵山大佛】（不含吉祥颂演出）：20 年来，灵山景区俨然已成了古城无锡的旅游新标地，祈福礼佛的好去处，以致世人尊称为 &ldquo;灵山胜境&rdquo;。其中高达 88 米的中国大佛，灵山大佛，更使无数善男信女趋之若鹜。灵不灵，就看你自己的感觉了。（自理：210 元 / 人）【备注；不参加自费的客人，自行在景区外游玩】</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">游览神州大佛【灵山大佛】（约 2.5 小时）；参观八十八米高露天青铜释迦牟尼佛立像，观九龙灌浴（佛祖释迦牟尼诞生时的宏大场面）、阿育王柱、菩提大道等，摸佛手、求福寿，参观第二届世界佛教论坛举办地、有东方卢浮宫之称的&mdash;&mdash;灵山梵宫，深度体验佛教文化。（景区内不含灵山电瓶车 25 元 / 人，需自理）</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photos\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo detail-journey-photo-2\" style=\"margin: 0px -10px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none; width: 350px; height: 225px;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G2/M00/AE/2D/Cii-TlgAW1mIWaEIAAYshqnIfvQAADXjAKTRsEABiye890_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G2/M00/AE/2D/Cii-TlgAW1mIWaEIAAYshqnIfvQAADXjAKTRsEABiye890_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"灵山大佛\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 350px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none; width: 350px; height: 225px;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G2/M00/AE/2E/Cii-TFgAW5CIStAnAA51y7fweoMAADXjQBBlrMADnXj462_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G2/M00/AE/2E/Cii-TFgAW5