中山先生的陵墓【中山陵】（游览时间：约 2 小时）</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\">景点介绍：中山陵</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">中山陵是中国近代民主革命先行者孙中山的陵墓，及其附属纪念建筑群，面积为 8 万余平方米。中山陵位于南京市东郊钟山风景名胜区内，东毗灵谷寺，西邻明孝陵，整个建筑群依山势而建，由南往北沿中轴线逐渐升高，主要建筑有牌坊、墓道、陵门、石阶、碑亭、祭堂和墓室等，排列在一条中轴线上，体现了中国传统建筑的风格，从空中往下看，像一座平卧在绿绒毯上的 &ldquo;自由钟&rdquo;，被誉为 &ldquo;中国近代建筑史上第 一陵&rdquo;（周一陵墓例行关闭检修，如遇关闭自动取消该点；景交车 20 元 / 人，需自理）</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photos\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo detail-journey-photo-2\" style=\"margin: 0px -10px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none; width: 350px; height: 225px;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G2/M00/AC/31/Cii-TFf_Jy-IP_ZtAAYeyHJPz2gAADVNAEPspkABh7g871_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G2/M00/AC/31/Cii-TFf_Jy-IP_ZtAAYeyHJPz2gAADVNAEPspkABh7g871_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"中山陵\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 350px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none; width: 350px; height: 225px;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/D5/1D/Cii9EVarGsiINLCyAAfL_60z9f8AABrkQI38ToAB8wX746_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/D5/1D/Cii9EVarGsiINLCyAAfL_60z9f8AABrkQI38ToAB8wX746_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"中山陵\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 350px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-feature-photo-sep\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\"><span class=\"detail-journey-time\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -110px; top: 5px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 12px; text-align: center; line-height: 20px; background-image: url(&quot;/static/img/201611/modules/tour/tour/icons-s03a8f95e63.png&quot;); background-position: -78px -212px; background-repeat: no-repeat; overflow: visible; display: inline-block; height: 20px; width: 55px;\">约 10:00</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">【夫子庙秦淮风光带】（自由活动约 2 个小时）</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\">景点介绍：夫子庙秦淮风光带</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">夫子庙秦淮风光带位于南京市秦淮区境内，以夫子庙为核心、十里秦淮为轴线，串联起东水关、白鹭洲公园、夫子庙、江南贡院、瞻园等，包括秦淮河两岸的街巷、民居、附近的古迹，面积约 4.69 平方公 里。夫子庙秦淮风光带是以 &ldquo;十里秦淮&rdquo;、明城墙风光、夫子庙为景观特色，以儒家思想与科举文化、民俗文化等为内涵，集旅游观光、美食购物、科普教育、节庆 文化等功能于一体，是中国著名的开放式 5A 级旅游景区。</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\"><span class=\"detail-journey-time\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -110px; top: 5px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 12px; text-align: center; line-height: 20px; background-image: url(&quot;/static/img/201611/modules/tour/tour/icons-s03a8f95e63.png&quot;); background-position: -78px -212px; background-repeat: no-repeat; overflow: visible; display: inline-block; height: 20px; width: 55px;\">约 13:00</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">午餐后前往全国爱国教育基地、侵华日军南京大屠杀遇难同胞纪念馆【南京大屠杀纪念馆】</div>\r\n<div class=\"detai