n class=\"detail-journey-time\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -110px; top: 5px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 12px; text-align: center; line-height: 20px; background-image: url(&quot;/static/img/201611/modules/tour/tour/icons-s03a8f95e63.png&quot;); background-position: -78px -212px; background-repeat: no-repeat; overflow: visible; display: inline-block; height: 20px; width: 55px;\">约 6:30</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">酒店叫早，享用早餐</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\"><span class=\"detail-journey-time\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -110px; top: 5px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 12px; text-align: center; line-height: 20px; background-image: url(&quot;/static/img/201611/modules/tour/tour/icons-s03a8f95e63.png&quot;); background-position: -78px -212px; background-repeat: no-repeat; overflow: visible; display: inline-block; height: 20px; width: 55px;\">约 7:30</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">赠送《非诚勿扰》拍摄地，陆游江南最后一片湿地【西溪国家湿地公园二期】(不含游船和电瓶车）（游览时间：约 20 分钟）。</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\">景点介绍：西溪国家湿地公园二期</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">西溪，古称河渚，&ldquo;曲水弯环，群山四绕，名园古刹，前后踵接，又多芦汀沙溆&rdquo;。历史上的西溪占地约 60 平方公里，现实施保护的西溪湿地总面积约为 11.5 平方公里，分为东部湿地生态保护培育区、中部湿地生态旅游休闲区和西部湿地生态景观封育区。在 2012 年 1 月 10 日，杭州西溪国家湿地公园荣升国家 5A 级旅游景区。高庄园林，福堤，逛河渚街感受水乡民俗，感受满眼是清淡雅致的绿和微波荡漾的水&hellip;&hellip; 后赴上海。</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photos\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo detail-journey-photo-2\" style=\"margin: 0px -10px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none; width: 350px; height: 225px;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/D1/DF/Cii9EFapx1mINcuzAAb68pR2w_UAABqgwPtEqoABvsK293_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/D1/DF/Cii9EFapx1mINcuzAAb68pR2w_UAABqgwPtEqoABvsK293_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"西溪湿地二期\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 350px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none; width: 350px; height: 225px;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/filebroker/cdn/vnd/19/2d/192dabe3a83401a8051b8345b96eaf7e_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/filebroker/cdn/vnd/19/2d/192dabe3a83401a8051b8345b96eaf7e_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"西溪湿地\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 350px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-feature-photo-sep\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\"><span class=\"detail-journey-time\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -110px; top: 5px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 12px; text-align: center; line-height: 20px; background-image: url(&quot;/static/img/201611/modules/tour/tour/icons-s03a8f95e63.png&quot;); background-position: -78px -212px; background-repeat: no-repeat; overflow: visible; display: inline-block; height: 20px; width: 55px;\">约 8:30</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">车赴西湖景区（约 1.5 小时）游览【西湖】</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\">景点介绍：西湖</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">无限美好风光。西湖古称 &ldquo;钱塘湖&rdquo;，又名 &ldquo;西子湖&rdquo;，古代诗人苏轼就对它评价道：&ldquo;欲把西湖比西子，淡妆浓抹总相宜。&rdquo; 西湖形态为近于等轴的多边形，湖面被孤山及苏堤、白堤两条人工堤分割为 5 个子湖区，子湖区间由桥孔连通，各部分的湖水不能充分掺混，造成各湖区水质差异，大部分径流补给先进入西侧 3 个子湖区，再进入外西湖。阳春三月，莺飞草长。苏白两堤，桃柳夹岸。两边是水波潋滟，游船点点，远处是山色空蒙，青黛含翠。此时走在堤上，你会被眼前的景色所惊叹，甚至心醉神驰，怀疑自己是否进入了世外仙境。 而西湖的美景不仅春天独有，夏日里接天莲碧的荷花，秋夜中浸透月光的三潭，冬雪后疏影横斜的红梅，更有那烟柳笼纱中的莺啼，细雨迷蒙中的楼台 ------ 无论你在何时来，都会领略到不同寻常的风采。</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photos\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo detail-journey-photo-2\" style=\"margin: 0px -10px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none; width: 350px; height: 225px;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G2/M00/AC/1C/Cii-T1f_INGIHGYZAAJYGwnXHTAAADVIgPuX-gAAlgz503_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G2/M00/AC/1C/Cii-T1f_INGIHGYZAAJYGwnXHTAAADVIgPuX-gAAlgz503_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"西湖\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 350px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none; width: 350px; height: 225px;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G2/M00/AC/0F/Cii-T1f_HAaIX1YZAAOwTT7EAH0AADVFAKyLEwAA7Bl903_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G2/M00/AC/0F/Cii-T1f_HAaIX1YZAAOwTT7EAH0AADVFAKyLEwAA7Bl903_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"西湖\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 350px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-feature-photo-sep\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\"><span class=\"detail-journey-time\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -110px; top: 5px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 12px; text-align: center; line-height: 20px; background-image: url(&quot;/static/img/201611/modules/tour/tour/icons-s03a8f95e63.png&quot;); background-position: -78px -212px; background-repeat: no-repeat; overflow: visible; display: inline-block; height: 20px; width: 55px;\">约 10：00</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">参观位于杭州西子湖畔的【丝绸文化博物馆】（约 1 小时）</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\">景点介绍：丝绸文化博物馆</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">是座全国性的丝绸专业博物馆，感受了解中国丝绸发展的历史和故事。（注：此处可能有购物，不强制消费，如需购物，请索要发票。如因游客购物造成时间延长，延长时间不计入旅行社的客观安排停留时间）</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\"><span class=\"detail-journey-time\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -110px; top: 5px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 12px; text-align: center; line-height: 20px; background-image: url(&quot;/static/img/201611/modules/tour/tour/icons-s03a8f95e63.png&quot;); background-position: -78px -212px; background-repeat: no-repeat; overflow: visible; display: inline-block; height: 20px; width: 55px;\">约 13:00</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">中餐后车赴乌镇游览国家 AAAAA 级景区<span class=\"_0000FF\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255) !important;\"><b>【乌镇】<br />\r\n</b></span></div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\">景点介绍：乌镇</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">在乌镇有人说语言似乎是多余的，因为它这里的文化气氛太厚重：潺潺的流水，静静的枕河人家，青青的石板路，木雕镂空的门窗，素雅的蓝印花布&hellip;&hellip; 就像一首浪漫寂静的散文诗，让人不忍心破坏这种意境和美感。这里商业化气氛不浓：街道两旁是最最普通的平民住宅，有些居民的门窗敞开，见惯了络绎的游客，对好奇的目光坦然了然。老人们仍旧是低头打扫自己的房间，或者搬了小木板凳坐到街边的阳光下晒太阳。江南最知名水乡，参观矛盾故居、林家铺子、百床馆、钱币馆等。</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\"><span class=\"detail-journey-time\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -110px; top: 5px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 12px; text-align: center; line-height: 20px; background-image: url(&quot;/static/img/201611/modules/tour/tour/icons-s03a8f95e63.png&quot;); background-position: -78px -212px; background-repeat: no-repeat; overflow: visible; display: inline-block; height: 20px; width: 55px;\">约 15:00</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">车赴江南园林城市&mdash;苏州，游览有着 900 多年的悠久历史，中国 AAAAA 水乡【周庄】</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\">景点介绍：周庄</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">它是一座江南小镇，有 &ldquo;中国水乡&rdquo; 之誉，是国家首批 5A 级景区。周庄始建于 1086 年（北宋元祐元年），因邑人周迪功先生捐地修全福寺而得名。江南六大古镇之一，于 2003 年被评为中国历史文化名镇，是典型的江南水乡风貌，有独特的人文景观，是中国水乡文化和吴地汉文化的瑰宝。周庄镇 60% 以上的民居仍为明清建筑，仅 0.47 平方公里的古镇有近百座古典宅院和 60 多个砖雕门楼，周庄民居古风犹存，还保存了 14 座各具特色的古桥。游览张厅、沈厅、江南明清时期水乡名宅的典型代表、体会千年古桥百年老屋小桥水的水乡魅力！</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photos\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo detail-journey-photo-2\" style=\"margin: 0px -10px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none; width: 350px; height: 225px;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G2/M00/4F/A6/Cii-TFfD5L-IfpelAAOkDJOlUssAAB1NwNaZHoAA6Qk697_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G2/M00/4F/A6/Cii-TFfD5L-IfpelAAOkDJOlUssAAB1NwNaZHoAA6Qk697_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"周庄夜景\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 350px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 381px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none; width: 350px; height: 225px;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/filebroker/cdn/vnd/da/2a/da2a8b5eb87a07a9f5cad60447855622_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/filebroker/cdn/vnd/da/2a/da2a8b5eb87a07a9f5cad60447855622_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"周庄\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 350px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-feature-photo-sep\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-style: dotted; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px;\">餐饮</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-list\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">早餐：含 午餐：含 晚餐：自理</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\" s