=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; float: right; display: inline;\"><a poiid=\"10558650\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\"><img poiid=\"10558650\" title=\"天门山国家森林公园\" src=\"https://dimg08.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g4/M06/7E/BB/CggYHlaCNHOAF7EvACvCUsqTaq4190_C_210_118.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; width: 210px; height: 118px; vertical-align: top; cursor: pointer; opacity: 1;\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n    <h6 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\"><a poiid=\"10558650\" title=\"天门山国家森林公园\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\">天门山国家森林公园</a></h6>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\">天门山国家森林公园四面绝壁，雄伟壮丽。保存着完整的原始次生林，植物资源丰富，有世界罕见的高山珙桐群落。天门山文化底蕴深厚，留有大量赞咏天门山的诗词，更有众多神闻传说，被誉为 &ldquo;张家界之魂&rdquo;。</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"day_scene_list\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1; border-top: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204);\">\r\n    <div class=\"scene_pic\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; float: right; display: inline;\"><a poiid=\"20940931\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\"><img poiid=\"20940931\" title=\"天门山玻璃栈道\" src=\"https://dimg01.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M0B/76/56/CggYG1aCLoqAZen_ABt2ILCFy8w877_C_210_118.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; width: 210px; height: 118px; vertical-align: top; cursor: pointer; opacity: 1;\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n    <h6 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\"><a poiid=\"20940931\" title=\"天门山玻璃栈道\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\">天门山玻璃栈道</a></h6>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\">玻璃栈道，是天门山内的精华特色游道。西线栈道全长 60 米，先运营；东线栈道全长 150 米，后运营。栈道都建在悬崖峭壁上，道路全部用透明玻璃建成，走在上面，看到脚下的万丈深谷，胆战心惊之余，感受凌空行走的快乐。 在天气比较恶劣时，比如下雨，玻璃栈道将被关闭运营。</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"day_scene_list\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1; border-top: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204);\">\r\n    <div class=\"scene_pic\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; float: right; display: inline;\"><a poiid=\"15041322\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\"><img poiid=\"15041322\" title=\"鬼谷栈道\" src=\"https://dimg07.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M02/78/1C/CggYGVaCLCKAfTZEACz1O66bHS0330_C_210_118.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; width: 210px; height: 118px; vertical-align: top; cursor: pointer; opacity: 1;\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n    <h6 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\"><a poiid=\"15041322\" title=\"鬼谷栈道\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\">鬼谷栈道</a></h6>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\">鬼谷栈道位于天门山国家森林公园内，因悬于鬼谷洞上侧的峭壁沿线而得名。栈道起倚虹关，止于小天门，全长 1600 米，平均海拔 1400 米。这条栈道既不在悬崖之巅，也不在悬崖之侧，而是全线都立于万丈悬崖的中间，而其中最惊险、最刺激的一段则是海拔最高处的 &ldquo;天空之路&rdquo;。这段长 60 米，宽 1.6 米的玻璃栈道悬空在海拔 1400 米以上的山崖间，非常透明，低头就能看见倒映在脚下的蓝天白云，让人心跳加速。站在栈道之上，脚下是成群的飞鸟，眼前是辽阔的山野，成群的小鸟在峡谷中嬉戏。距栈道终点不远处，还有一个凌空伸出的长约 5 米的玻璃站台，没有钢筋水泥的阻碍，只有赤裸裸的透明，这种非比寻常赏景的方式真不是一般人能 &ldquo;享受&rdquo; 到的。另外在栈道的完结处的两个悬崖之间有一条长 160 米的悬索吊桥，刺激一重接着一重，想不尖叫都难。</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"day_scene_list\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1; border-top: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204);\">\r\n    <div class=\"scene_pic\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; float: right; display: inline;\"><a poiid=\"10543152\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\"><img poiid=\"10543152\" title=\"李娜别墅\" src=\"https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M04/78/83/CggYGVaCLl6AHus7ABUNoSiwJow666_C_210_118.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; width: 210px; height: 118px; vertical-align: top; cursor: pointer; opacity: 1;\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n    <h6 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\"><a poiid=\"10543152\" title=\"李娜别墅\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\">李娜别墅</a></h6>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\">李娜别墅位于天门山国家森林公园内，乘坐天门山索道到上站，出门后第一个景点即是。这是一栋二层木屋，石板铺砌的平地上，一大块红砂岩的正面书刻着 &ldquo;李娜别墅&rdquo; 四个大字。1997 年因一曲《青藏高原》而走红的歌手李娜游览天门山时，被这里的清净安宁打动，于是迁居此处，并修建了一座小木屋。但是她只居住了一个月就将小屋送给天门山管理处，自己在五台山出家为尼。天门山管理处将李娜小屋改建成为豪华大院，更名为 &ldquo;李娜别墅&rdquo;。现在的李娜别墅早已无人居住，门外的走廊成为游客的休憩之地。然而这样一座小屋在天门山壮观的自然景观中却是独特的存在，也许夏天去并不会发现它的美，但是如果冬天到这里，你便会觉得这座小屋真的是皑皑白雪中最好的点缀。尤其是站在云梦仙顶俯瞰，被白雪覆盖的林木中间，独独露出一栋彩色的小屋，为这单调的灰、白增添了无限的情趣。</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">午餐：敬请自理。<br />\r\n    温馨提示：因天门山景区山顶没有餐厅，建议您当体可以自备一些干粮。</p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0px 0px -1px; padding: 20px 0px 6px 100px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); zoom: 1; overflow: hidden;\">\r\n    <h5 class=\"time_list\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -100px; padding: 0px; float: left; display: inline; font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px; width: 80px; overflow: hidden;\">14：30</h5>\r\n    <div class=\"day_detail\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 30px; border-left: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204); position: relative; zoom: 1; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.5;\">\r\n    <p class=\"bg_important\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px 5px; line-height: 22px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); display: inline-block;\">行驶距离: 约 265 公里 | 行驶时间: 约 4 小时 | 游览时间: 约 30 分钟</p>\r\n    <div class=\" day_scene_list border_none\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px; border-top: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204); border-right: 0px none !important; border-bottom: 0px none !important; border-left: 0px none !important; border-image: initial !important; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\">\r\n    <div class=\"scene_pic\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; float: right; display: inline;\"><a poiid=\"10558753\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\"><img poiid=\"10558753\" title=\"凤凰古城\" src=\"https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g2/M09/8B/46/Cghzf1Ww3-SAKZ_uACYRYW8dQE8796_C_210_118.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; width: 210px; height: 118px; vertical-align: top; cursor: pointer; opacity: 1;\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n    <h6 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\"><a poiid=\"10558753\" title=\"凤凰古城\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\">凤凰古城</a></h6>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\">游览完天门山国家森林公园后，集合乘车前往中国最美丽的古城&mdash;&mdash; 【<a href=\"https://vpn1.ctrip.com/prx/000/http/travel.ctrip.com/jingdian-7467.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\">凤凰古城</a>】。</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0px 0px -1px; padding: 20px 0px 6px 100px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); zoom: 1; overflow: hidden;\">\r\n    <h5 class=\"time_list\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -100px; padding: 0px; float: left; display: inline; font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px; width: 80px; overflow: hidden;\">17：30</h5>\r\n    <div class=\"day_detail\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 30px; border-left: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204); position: relative; zoom: 1; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.5;\">\r\n    <p class=\"bg_important\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px 5px; line-height: 22px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); display: inline-block;\">用餐时间: 约 1 小时</p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">晚餐: 参考餐厅：土苗情餐厅（庆功宴），（围桌团餐，餐标 20 元 / 人）。<br />\r\n    参考菜单：土家迎宾茶、湘西土匪鸭干锅、玉米海带火锅、霸王猪脸、猛洞河野生河虾、肉末豆腐、湘西土家腊肉、农家小炒肉、刘晓庆米豆腐每人一小碗、野菜粑粑每人一个、湘西外婆菜、清炒时令小菜、水晶萝卜、麻辣小鱼、水果拼盘。<br />\r\n    （以上菜单仅供参考，每桌限 10 人，如人数不足，菜品和数量会相应的减少，敬请谅解）。</p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0px 0px -1px; padding: 20px 0px 6px 100px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); zoom: 1; overflow: hidden;\">\r\n    <h5 class=\"time_list\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -100px; padding: 0px; float: left; display: inline; font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px; width: 80px; overflow: hidden;\">20：00</h5>\r\n    <div class=\"day_detail\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 30px; border-left: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204); position: relative; zoom: 1; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.5;\">\r\n    <p class=\"bg_important\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px 5px; line-height: 22px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); display: inline-block;\">活动时间: 约 30 分钟</p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">前往酒店:&nbsp;<a hotelid=\"879403\" hotel=\"true\" title=\"凤凰黄金岛大酒店\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\">凤凰黄金岛大酒店</a>&nbsp;或&nbsp;<a hotelid=\"844996\" hotel=\"true\" title=\"凤凰火凤大酒店\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\">凤凰火凤大酒店</a>&nbsp;或&nbsp;<a hotelid=\"808948\" hotel=\"true\" title=\"凤凰县凯盛大酒店\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\">凤凰县凯盛大酒店</a>&nbsp;或&nbsp;<a hotelid=\"1372073\" hotel=\"true\" title=\"凤凰凤都大酒店\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\">凤凰凤都大酒店</a></p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">参考房型：双人标准间。</p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0px 0px -1px; padding: 20px 0px 6px 100px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); zoom: 1; overflow: hidden;\">\r\n    <h5 class=\"time_list\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -100px; padding: 0px; float: left; display: inline; font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px; width: 80px; overflow: hidden;\">20：30</h5>\r\n    <div class=\"day_detail\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 30px; border-left: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204); position: relative; zoom: 1; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.5;\">\r\n    <p class=\"bg_important\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px 5px; line-height: 22px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); display: inline-block;\">游览时间: 约 2 小时</p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">自由活动:</p>\r\n    <div class=\" day_scene_list border_none\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px; border-top: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204); border-right: 0px none !important; border-bottom: 0px none !important; border-left: 0px none !important; border-image: initial !important; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\">\r\n    <div class=\"scene_pic\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; float: right; display: inline;\"><a poiid=\"10558753\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\"><img poiid=\"10558753\" title=\"凤凰古城\" src=\"https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g2/M09/8B/46/Cghzf1Ww3-SAKZ_uACYRYW8dQE8796_C_210_118.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; width: 210px; height: 118px; vertical-align: top; cursor: pointer; opacity: 1;\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n    <h6 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\"><a poiid=\"10558753\" title=\"凤凰古城\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\">凤凰古城</a>&nbsp;<span class=\"grey\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\"><font color=\"green\"><b>（观赏夜景）</b></font></span></h6>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\">办理完入住手续后，是自由休闲的时光。您可以选择逛逛江边的酒吧也可前往小吃街品尝当地特色小吃，尽情享受这份美妙时光！</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"day_list\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 1px solid rgb(229, 229, 229); zoom: 1; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n<div class=\"day_title\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px 0px 120px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(229, 229, 229); background: rgb(247, 247, 247); overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\"><a id=\"route_day4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); outline: none; margin-top: -136px; position: absolute;\">&nbsp;</a>\r\n<h5 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -100px; padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 22px; line-height: 42px; zoom: 1; overflow: hidden; float: left; display: inline;\">第 4 天</h5>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 22px; line-height: 42px; zoom: 1; overflow: hidden;\">游览中国最美丽的古城&mdash;凤凰古城，沱江泛舟，下午长沙自由活动、入住酒店</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"day_content\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; zoom: 1; overflow: hidden;\">\r\n<ul class=\"day_con_list\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0px 0px -1px; padding: 20px 0px 6px 100px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); zoom: 1; overflow: hidden;\">\r\n    <h5 class=\"time_list\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -100px; padding: 0px; float: left; display: inline; font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px; width: 80px; overflow: hidden;\">07：00</h5>\r\n    <div class=\"day_detail\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 30px; border-left: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204); position: relative; zoom: 1; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.5;\">\r\n    <p class=\"bg_important\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px 5px; line-height: 22px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); display: inline-block;\">用餐时间: 约 30 分钟</p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">早餐: 所住酒店内（自助式）。</p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0px 0px -1px; padding: 20px 0px 6px 100px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); zoom: 1; overflow: hidden;\">\r\n    <h5 class=\"time_list\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -100px; padding: 0px; float: left; display: inline; font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px; width: 80px; overflow: hidden;\">07：30</h5>\r\n    <div class=\"day_detail\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 30px; border-left: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204); position: relative; zoom: 1; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.5;\">\r\n    <p class=\"bg_important\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px 5px; line-height: 22px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); display: inline-block;\">游览时间: 约 4 小时</p>\r\n    <div class=\" day_scene_list border_none\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px; border-top: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204); border-right: 0px none !important; border-bottom: 0px none !important; border-left: 0px none !important; border-image: initial !important; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\">\r\n    <div class=\"scene_pic\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; float: right; display: inline;\"><a poiid=\"10558753\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\"><img poiid=\"10558753\" title=\"凤凰古城\" src=\"https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g2/M09/8B/46/Cghzf1Ww3-SAKZ_uACYRYW8dQE8796_C_210_118.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; width: 210px; height: 118px; vertical-align: top; cursor: pointer; opacity: 1;\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n    <h6 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\"><a poiid=\"10558753\" title=\"凤凰古城\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\">凤凰古城</a>&nbsp;<span class=\"grey\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">『游览古城九景』</span></h6>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\">凤凰古城是国家历史文化名城，是怀化、吉首、贵州铜仁三地之间的必经之路，它风景秀丽、历史悠久、名胜古迹甚多，自古以来一直是苗族和土家族的聚居地区。同样这里也是个人杰地灵的地方，代代才人辈出，使得自然风景和人文气息密切融合。</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"day_scene_list\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1; border-top: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204);\">\r\n    <div class=\"scene_pic\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; float: right; display: inline;\"><a poiid=\"90008\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\"><img poiid=\"90008\" title=\"崇德堂\" src=\"https://dimg08.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g4/M04/76/73/CggYHlYI-4mADeSnABzut6Rupyo999_C_210_118.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; width: 210px; height: 118px; vertical-align: top; cursor: pointer; opacity: 1;\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n    <h6 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\"><a poiid=\"90008\" title=\"崇德堂\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\">崇德堂</a></h6>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\">崇德堂位于凤凰古城中史家弄街，于 1884 年由当地首富裴守禄修建，其建筑规矩雅致，是一座全木结构的典型南方四合院。德堂距今已有百年历史，总面积 622 平方米，主要分为上下两层，第二层不对外开放。第一层是由一间石雕展厅、两间木雕展厅、中间会客厅和后方的餐厅以及后花园五个部分所组成。</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"day_scene_list\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1; border-top: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204);\">\r\n    <div class=\"scene_pic\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; float: right; display: inline;\"><a poiid=\"86933\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\"><img poiid=\"86933\" title=\"凤凰古城博物馆\" src=\"https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M01/70/64/CggYGVYI_luACRnAABcTdTLlSu4671_C_210_118.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; width: 210px; height: 118px; vertical-align: top; cursor: pointer; opacity: 1;\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n    <h6 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\"><a poiid=\"86933\" title=\"凤凰古城博物馆\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\">凤凰古城博物馆</a></h6>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\">古城博物馆原是陈宝箴世家的百年老宅，占地面积达 1600 多平方米，馆址范围即为清光绪年间道台衙门的组成部分，也是陈宝箴三代曾经生活过的地方。现在它是一个集古城博物馆、陈宝箴世家为一体的文化载体。</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"day_scene_list\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1; border-top: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204);\">\r\n    <div class=\"scene_pic\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; float: right; display: inline;\"><a poiid=\"80470\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\"><img poiid=\"80470\" title=\"沈从文故居\" src=\"https://dimg07.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g4/M05/76/A2/CggYHVYI_8SAE6vYABWX6taj-T4278_C_210_118.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; width: 210px; height: 118px; vertical-align: top; cursor: pointer; opacity: 1;\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n    <h6 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\"><a poiid=\"80470\" title=\"沈从文故居\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\">沈从文故居</a></h6>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\">沈从文生在凤凰古城中营街的一座典型的南方古四合院里。四合院是一座火砖封砌的平房建筑，始建于清同治五年，分前后两进，中有方块红石铺成的天井，左右配以古色古香的厢房，大小共 11 间，整座建筑具有浓郁的湘西明清建筑古城特色。故居于 1991 年被列为省人民政府重点文物保护单位。</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"day_scene_list\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1; border-top: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204);\">\r\n    <h6 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\"><a poiid=\"86925\" title=\"熊希龄故居\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\">熊希龄故居</a></h6>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\">熊希龄故居位于凤凰古城北文星街的一个小巷里，往东 200 米便是秀丽的沱江，总占地面积 800 平方米，为四合院系南方古式的木瓦结构，比较矮小但很精致，是典型的苗族古代建筑格式。</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"day_scene_list\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1; border-top: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204);\">\r\n    <div class=\"scene_pic\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; float: right; display: inline;\"><a poiid=\"86928\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\"><img poiid=\"86928\" title=\"杨家祠堂\" src=\"https://dimg07.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M06/70/FA/CggYG1YJAUOAEY88AB1yjfC_Moo181_C_210_118.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; width: 210px; height: 118px; vertical-align: top; cursor: pointer; opacity: 1;\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n    <h6 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\"><a poiid=\"86928\" title=\"杨家祠堂\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\">杨家祠堂</a></h6>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\">凤凰的祠堂，以田、杨两族的祠堂最大，而杨家祠堂也是凤凰城内保护最好的祠堂。祠堂位于古城沱江镇东门城楼和北门城楼之间，北边街史家弄入口处，堂占地 770 平方米。由太子太傅、果勇侯杨芳率族人于清道光十六年 (公元 1836 年) 开始建筑，且杨家本为名门旺族，祠堂建筑的规模并不比一般寺庙逊色。</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"day_scene_list\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1; border-top: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204);\">\r\n    <div class=\"scene_pic\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; float: right; display: inline;\"><a poiid=\"86935\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\"><img poiid=\"86935\" title=\"湘西东门城楼\" src=\"https://dimg03.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g2/M05/37/0C/Cghzf1Ubml2AVB5DAAk5PBH03x4817_C_210_118.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; width: 210px; height: 118px; vertical-align: top; cursor: pointer; opacity: 1;\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n    <h6 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\"><a poiid=\"86935\" title=\"湘西东门城楼\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\">湘西东门城楼</a></h6>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\">东门城楼位于凤凰古城东，面对东岭，紧靠沱江，古朴典雅，原名 &ldquo;升恒门&rdquo;，为凤凰古城四大城门之一，与不远处的北门城楼、南门城楼（南华门）曾一起护卫过这座美丽的山水小城。</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"day_scene_list\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1; border-top: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204);\">\r\n    <div class=\"scene_pic\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; float: right; display: inline;\"><a poiid=\"91381\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\"><img poiid=\"91381\" title=\"沱江跳岩\" src=\"https://dimg08.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g2/M0A/8B/46/Cghzf1Ww3-eAezd6ACUEIYDWDsw241_C_210_118.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; width: 210px; height: 118px; vertical-align: top; cursor: pointer; opacity: 1;\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n    <h6 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\"><a poiid=\"91381\" title=\"沱江跳岩\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\">沱江跳岩</a></h6>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\">沱江 &ldquo;跳岩&rdquo; 位于凤凰古城北门外沱江河道中，始建于清康熙四十三年（1704 年），旧时是东北向进出凤凰古城的主要通道之一。因人们经过时必须踩着这一路岩石，一跳一跳地过河去，&ldquo;跳岩&rdquo; 便因此而得名。</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"day_scene_list\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1; border-top: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204);\">\r\n    <div class=\"scene_pic\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; float: right; display: inline;\"><a poiid=\"86954\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\"><img poiid=\"86954\" title=\"万寿宫\" src=\"https://dimg07.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g4/M08/76/B8/CggYHVYJAPyAecnHACIlvQGR8i8251_C_210_118.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; width: 210px; height: 118px; vertical-align: top; cursor: pointer; opacity: 1;\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n    <h6 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\"><a poiid=\"86954\" title=\"万寿宫\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\">万寿宫</a></h6>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\">凤凰万寿宫又叫江西会馆，座落在风景秀丽的凤凰东门外沙湾，面临沱江，背靠青龙山，与百米外的古虹桥遥相对峙，所开的三门正对拱桥三孔，寓意财源似江水滚滚不息流进万寿宫。万寿宫是一处建筑规模宏大，设计精巧独特，雕琢玲珑剔透的建筑群落。</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"day_scene_list\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1; border-top: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204);\">\r\n    <div class=\"scene_pic\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; float: right; display: inline;\"><a poiid=\"86950\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\"><img poiid=\"86950\" title=\"虹桥风雨楼\" src=\"https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g2/M09/8B/46/Cghzf1Ww3-SAKZ_uACYRYW8dQE8796_C_210_118.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; width: 210px; height: 118px; vertical-align: top; cursor: pointer; opacity: 1;\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n    <h6 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\"><a poiid=\"86950\" title=\"虹桥风雨楼\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p5493785s28.html?kwd=%e5%bc%a0%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%8c###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\">虹桥风雨楼</a></h6>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\">虹桥原名卧虹桥，横卧于沱江之上，与民族一条街竖横交错，互为辉映。站在桥上可尽收沱江两岸如画风景，是凤凰古镇中观赏、摄影的最佳地之一。</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0px 0px -1px; padding: 20px 0px 6px 100px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); zoom: 1; overflow: hidden;\">\r\n    <h5 class=\"time_list\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -100px; padding: 0px; float: left; display: inline; font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px; width: 80px; overflow: hidden;\">12：00</h5>\r\n    <div class=\"day_detail\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 30px; border-left: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204); position: relative; zoom: 1; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.5;\">\r\n    <p class=\"bg_important\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px 5px; line-height: 22px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); display: inline-block;\">用餐时间: 约 1 小时</p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">午餐: 中式围桌团餐，餐标 20 元 / 人。<br />\r\n    三明主题餐厅，参考菜单：凤凰酸菜鱼火锅、玉米排骨火锅、苗家血粑鸭、土家香肠、土家扣肉、蒸土鸡蛋、清炒土豆丝、胡萝卜炒肉、家常豆腐、田园时蔬。<br />\r\n    （以上菜单仅供参考，每桌限 10 人，如人数不足，菜品和数量会相应的减少，敬请谅解）。</p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0px 0px -1px; padding: 20px 0px 6px 100px; list-style: 