x; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">亚龙湾海域清澈透明，海水能见度 6&mdash;27 米，是国内最佳潜水基地之一，也是中国十佳沙滩之一。粒洁白细软，海水澄澈晶莹，而且蔚蓝。终年可游泳，被誉为 &ldquo;天下第一湾&rdquo;。</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photos\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo detail-journey-photo-3\" style=\"margin: 0px -10px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 253.984px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: url(&quot;/static/img/2016/common/loading/72-72.gif&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"><img src=\"http://img4.tuniucdn.com/static/img/2016/common/placeholder.png\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/filebroker/cdn/snc/f6/96/f696dfb7ddad16aa8bc31dde56a34ce3_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"亚龙湾沙滩\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 233.984px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 253.984px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: url(&quot;/static/img/2016/common/loading/72-72.gif&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"><img src=\"http://img4.tuniucdn.com/static/img/2016/common/placeholder.png\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/filebroker/cdn/snc/e9/2c/e92c76fc082ba426d5343f987e8e6bd1_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"亚龙湾沙滩\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 233.984px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 253.984px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: url(&quot;/static/img/2016/common/loading/72-72.gif&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"><img src=\"http://img4.tuniucdn.com/static/img/2016/common/placeholder.png\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/filebroker/cdn/snc/ed/4e/ed4e0cc9bf37bf5705c3c98b2f2acf50_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"亚龙湾沙滩\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 233.984px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-feature-photo-sep\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-style: dotted; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17);\">★今日温馨小贴士</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">1、亚龙湾是以大海、沙滩等自然景观为主，游览时为自由活动，请注意游览时间，在导游规定的地点准时集合。沙滩上日照强烈，温度高，请做好防晒工作，请携带好防晒霜（最好防水型），遮阳帽，遮阳伞等遮阳用品。<br />\r\n2、呀诺达雨林文化旅游区热带植物众多，同时也蚊虫较多，请游览前涂抹好驱虫液，以免蚊虫滋扰。</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-style: dotted; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17);\">晚餐：海南四大名菜（60 / 人餐标）<span class=\"detail-journey-time\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -110px; top: 5px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 12px; text-align: center; line-height: 20px; background-image: url(&quot;/static/img/201611/modules/tour/tour/icons-s03a8f95e63.png&quot;); background-position: -78px -212px; background-repeat: no-repeat; overflow: visible; display: inline-block; height: 20px; width: 55px;\">18:00</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">海南四大名菜菜单：海南椰子盅、清蒸和乐蟹、白切文昌鸡、卤味加积鸭、红烧东山羊、白灼中虾、清蒸红宝石、粉丝蒸扇贝、香辣海鱼肚、海南全家福、清炒时蔬、椰子饭、馒头、水果盘。（以上菜单仅供参考，根据季节不同有可能会稍作调整）</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-style: dotted; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17);\">TIPS: 四大名菜为围桌餐，由于餐标人数限制，如当日团期团队人数不足 8 人，则无法安排，届时将由导游现退餐费 60 元 / 人，敬请谅解！</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-style: dotted; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17);\">行程结束之后返回酒店后自由活动</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-style: dotted; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17);\">可选入住酒店：三亚福朋喜来登酒店 / 三亚国光豪生度假酒店 / 三亚京海国际假日酒店 / 三亚华宇亚龙湾迎宾馆</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-style: dotted; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"J_JourneyDay3\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-head\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 15px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; position: relative; line-height: 26px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\"><span class=\"icon detail-journey-day\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -57px; top: -5px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 36px; font-size: 16px; background-image: url(&quot;/static/img/201611/modules/tour/tour/icons-s03a8f95e63.png&quot;); background-position: -126px -480px; background-repeat: no-repeat; overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; height: 47px; width: 40px;\">D3</span>蜈支洲岛一天</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17);\">早餐：酒店用自助早餐<span class=\"detail-journey-time\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -110px; top: 5px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 12px; text-align: center; line-height: 20px; background-image: url(&quot;/static/img/201611/modules/tour/tour/icons-s03a8f95e63.png&quot;); background-position: -78px -212px; background-repeat: no-repeat; overflow: visible; display: inline-block; height: 20px; width: 55px;\">7:30</span>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-duration\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">(用餐时间：约 60 分钟)</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-style: dotted; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17);\">酒店&nbsp;&nbsp;蜈支洲岛</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-note\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">乘车前往蜈支洲岛纯玩海一整天（含上下岛时间不少于 5 小时），车程约 60 分钟左右</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-style: dotted; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17);\"><a data-id=\"4780\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 194, 51);\">4A 级 蜈支洲岛</a><span class=\"detail-journey-time\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -110px; top: 5px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 12px; text-align: center; line-height: 20px; background-image: url(&quot;/static/img/201611/modules/tour/tour/icons-s03a8f95e63.png&quot;); background-position: -78px -212px; background-repeat: no-repeat; overflow: visible; display: inline-block; height: 20px; width: 55px;\">9:30</span>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-duration\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">(游览时间：约 300 分钟)</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">【蜈支洲岛】是中国极佳的潜水基地，是世界上为数不多的唯一没有礁石或者鹅卵石混杂的海岛，这里海岸线蜿蜒绵长，零污染的海水清澈见底，沙质洁白细腻，恍若玉带天成。在这里您可以选择下海嬉水或者玩水上项目 ^^；我们安排的预览时间较充足，如果您想要深入玩岛：<br />\r\n途牛小编推荐游览线路：情人桥&mdash;&mdash;白沙滩&mdash;&mdash;观日岩（距离较远需自费坐电瓶车）&mdash;&mdash;《私人订制》淡水泳池</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photos\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo detail-journey-photo-3\" style=\"margin: 0px -10px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 253.984px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: url(&quot;/static/img/2016/common/loading/72-72.gif&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"><img src=\"http://img4.tuniucdn.com/static/img/2016/common/placeholder.png\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/filebroker/cdn/snc/42/e7/42e7fadd7b99a2209a02758efbfd6ea7_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"蜈支洲岛\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 233.984px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 253.984px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: url(&quot;/static/img/2016/common/loading/72-72.gif&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"><img src=\"http://img4.tuniucdn.com/static/img/2016/common/placeholder.png\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/filebroker/cdn/snc/4d/0c/4d0c53289c2b21c898a0d02b1b556ec8_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"蜈支洲岛\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 233.984px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 253.984px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: url(&quot;/static/img/2016/common/loading/72-72.gif&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"><img src=\"http://img4.tuniucdn.com/static/img/2016/common/placeholder.png\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/47/5F/Cii9EFd7rXCIRPMyAAyG2JWa1nYAAG8XQBLzEkADIbw673_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"蜈支洲岛\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 233.984px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-feature-photo-sep\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-style: dotted; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17);\"><a data-id=\"0\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 194, 51);\">蜈支洲 - 情人桥</a></div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">【情人桥】此处为贺岁片《私人订制》重要拍摄地，原是座铁索桥，是当年守岛部队的海上了望点。走在铁索桥上摇摇晃晃的，需要几分胆量和机灵。有些小姐既想过桥到了望点体验一下，又怕掉进海水里，过桥时紧紧抓住朋友的手不放，因此这桥又被戏称为 &ldquo;情人桥&rdquo;。后来为客人安全着想，将原来的铁索桥改造成现在的木板桥。这里依旧成为情侣们最向往的地方。</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photos\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo detail-journey-photo-3\" style=\"margin: 0px -10px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 253.984px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/47/5E/Cii9EVd7rSGIVOJSAAMJGFB6IvUAAG8XAKQ4SgAAwkw451_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/47/5E/Cii9EVd7rSGIVOJSAAMJGFB6IvUAAG8XAKQ4SgAAwkw451_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"蜈支洲-情人桥\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 233.984px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 253.984px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/47/5E/Cii9EFd7rSWIXSqoAAFLP9qYnUUAAG8XAKYCNcAAUtX070_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/47/5E/Cii9EFd7rSWIXSqoAAFLP9qYnUUAAG8XAKYCNcAAUtX070_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"蜈支洲-情人桥\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 233.984px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 253.984px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/47/5E/Cii9EFd7rSmIEPQpAAdmdD6EXgoAAG8XAKokG4AB2aM957_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/47/5E/Cii9EFd7rSmIEPQpAAdmdD6EXgoAAG8XAKokG4AB2aM957_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"蜈支洲-情人桥\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 233.984px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-feature-photo-sep\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-style: dotted; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17);\"><a data-id=\"0\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 194, 51);\">蜈支洲 - 白沙滩</a></div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">【白沙滩】蜈支洲岛上，所有的一切都是晶莹剔透的，海浪一层层冲上海滩，雪白的浪花永远洗刷着雪白的珊瑚沙。与心爱的人走在洁白的沙滩上，真是让人流连忘返</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photos\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo detail-journey-photo-3\" style=\"margin: 0px -10px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 253.984px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/47/5E/Cii9EVd7rQiIE9HgAEZillwzC54AAG8XAGZd74ARmKu607_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/47/5E/Cii9EVd7rQiIE9HgAEZillwzC54AAG8XAGZd74ARmKu607_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"蜈支洲-白沙滩\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 233.984px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 253.984px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/47/5E/Cii9EVd7rQyIaFDkAAH1DvAFEWYAAG8XAIRa54AAfUm897_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/47/5E/Cii9EVd7rQyIaFDkAAH1DvAFEWYAAG8XAIRa54AAfUm897_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"蜈支洲-白沙滩\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 233.984px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 253.984px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/47/5E/Cii9EVd7rQ-ILhDkAAG0SUJtwRcAAG8XAI5mQQAAbRh812_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/47/5E/Cii9EVd7rQ-ILhDkAAG0SUJtwRcAAG8XAI5mQQAAbRh812_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"蜈支洲-白沙滩\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 233.984px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-feature-photo-sep\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-style: dotted; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17);\"><a data-id=\"0\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 194, 51);\">蜈支洲 - 观日岩</a></div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">【观日岩】观日岩位于蜈支洲岛的东南悬崖处。站在岩上凭海临风，俯瞰全岛，辽阔的南海尽收眼底。悬崖下面，怪石嶙峋。风平浪静之时，乘快艇环岛游，石景千奇百怪，观日岩像一尊天然大石佛，面向大海，日夜修炼。观日岩又像一只巨龟缓缓爬向大海，期望回到自己的故乡，故又称金龟探海。新世纪的第一缕曙光从这里升起，绯红的太阳从海面上徐徐上升，形成一绝佳的海上观日点。</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photos\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo detail-journey-photo-3\" style=\"margin: 0px -10px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 253.984px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/47/5E/Cii9EVd7rO2Ie2hpAC8HSw8hHQYAAG8XAAAAAAALwdj777_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/47/5E/Cii9EVd7rO2Ie2hpAC8HSw8hHQYAAG8XAAAAAAALwdj777_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"蜈支洲-观日岩\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 233.984px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 253.984px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/47/5E/Cii9EVd7rPGIN5TRAAqv20biAuAAAG8XACj0g4ACq_z160_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/47/5E/Cii9EVd7rPGIN5TRAAqv20biAuAAAG8XACj0g4ACq_z160_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"蜈支洲-观日岩\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 233.984px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 253.984px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner loaded\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: none;\"><img src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/47/5E/Cii9EFd7rPWIBYIqAAOCTaqxfHwAAG8XAC1hssAA4J