ney-title\" style=\"margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17);\">晚餐：西安饭庄&mdash;&mdash;陕西特色小吃套餐（泡馍、biangbiang 面，肉夹馍、面皮等）（餐标 58 元 / 人）<span class=\"detail-journey-time\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -110px; top: 5px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 12px; text-align: center; line-height: 20px; background-image: url(&quot;/static/img/201611/modules/tour/tour/icons-s03a8f95e63.png&quot;); background-position: -78px -212px; background-repeat: no-repeat; overflow: visible; display: inline-block; height: 20px; width: 55px;\">17:00</span>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-duration\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">(用餐时间：约 60 分钟)</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">西安饭庄位于西安市繁华市区－东大街，于钟楼咫尺之距，交通便利。西安饭庄建于一九二九年，素以 &ldquo;陕菜正宗&rdquo;、&ldquo;陕西风味大全&rdquo; 闻名于世，曾接待过周恩来、叶剑英等党和国家领导人，张学良、杨虎城等爱国将领及老舍、柳青等文化名流。<br />\r\n2014 年 2 月 18 日，中共中央总书记习近平会见中国国民党荣誉主席连战，在北京钓鱼台国宾馆养源斋设家宴款待连战伉俪。由于两人是陕西老乡，在席间还用家乡话交谈，家宴的饭菜则是陕西特色的羊肉泡馍、肉夹馍以及 &ldquo;biangbiang 面&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photos\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo detail-journey-photo-3\" style=\"margin: 0px -10px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 253.984px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: url(&quot;/static/img/2016/common/loading/72-72.gif&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"><img src=\"http://img2.tuniucdn.com/static/img/2016/common/placeholder.png\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/filebroker/cdn/snc/16/d7/16d751444e1496e128fa0117746454e8_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"羊肉泡馍（参考图片）\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 233.984px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 253.984px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: url(&quot;/static/img/2016/common/loading/72-72.gif&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"><img src=\"http://img2.tuniucdn.com/static/img/2016/common/placeholder.png\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/filebroker/cdn/snc/15/73/15733464dea77953891ffa9071e9c145_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"肉夹馍（参考图片）\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 233.984px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 253.984px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: url(&quot;/static/img/2016/common/loading/72-72.gif&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"><img src=\"http://img2.tuniucdn.com/static/img/2016/common/placeholder.png\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/filebroker/cdn/snc/67/5a/675a4f96b276536802fa7252a212a69c_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"biangbiang 面\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 233.984px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-feature-photo-sep\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-style: dotted; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17);\"><a data-id=\"4829\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 194, 51);\">回民小吃街</a><span class=\"detail-journey-time\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -110px; top: 5px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 12px; text-align: center; line-height: 20px; background-image: url(&quot;/static/img/201611/modules/tour/tour/icons-s03a8f95e63.png&quot;); background-position: -78px -212px; background-repeat: no-repeat; overflow: visible; display: inline-block; height: 20px; width: 55px;\">18:30</span>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-duration\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">(游览时间：约 60 分钟)</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">无论您是否西安人，您一定听说过西安回民小吃的大名。醇香诱人的羊肉泡馍，皮嫩汁浓的灌汤包子，透油发亮的黄桂柿子饼，可口香甜的八宝稀饭，提起这些享誉全国的西北小吃，别说外地朋友听了要慕名而来，就是本地人也一定馋得想流口水呢！主要的特色就是羊肉泡馍、烤肉、灌汤包及酸菜炒米（酸菜肉丝炒饭）配酸梅汤。这几样可是陕西的名小吃哦~ 在回民街的小吃店里一般都能叫到这些哦! 不过北方人都喜味重，所以不喜欢葱、姜、蒜的朋友可别忘了点菜的时候和服务员说明不要放这些东西哦~ 不然你会发现你点的食物里到处都有它们的影子哦, 当然还有不会吃辣的朋友。</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photos\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo detail-journey-photo-3\" style=\"margin: 0px -10px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 253.984px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: url(&quot;/static/img/2016/common/loading/72-72.gif&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"><img src=\"http://img2.tuniucdn.com/static/img/2016/common/placeholder.png\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/filebroker/cdn/snc/b1/63/b16305274a2f1d6ff7b44fc1713a4d56_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"回民一条街\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 233.984px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 253.984px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: url(&quot;/static/img/2016/common/loading/72-72.gif&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"><img src=\"http://img2.tuniucdn.com/st