n<br />\r\n重要通知：华山风景区为确保华山索道安全无事故运行，华山索道公司定于 2016 年 12 月 6 日 - 27 日对索道进行停运检修，12 月 28 日正常运营。在此期间出游的游客，华山北峰的索道费用将在我社折扣基础上导游现退，为此造成的不便，敬请广大游客谅解。（备注：华山西峰索道正常运行，行程中仅含华山北峰索道往返，需要登山的游客自愿选择西峰索道，费用差价请自理）</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photos\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo detail-journey-photo-3\" style=\"margin: 0px -10px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px -10px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 253.984px;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-photo-item-inner\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: url(&quot;/static/img/2016/common/loading/72-72.gif&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"><img src=\"http://img2.tuniucdn.com/static/img/2016/common/placeholder.png\" data-src=\"http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G2/M00/15/7F/Cii-TFgyTnyIOf1uABRylvpJDmYAAEowwCYkJ0AFHKu222_w500_h280_c1_t0.jpg\" alt=\"华山秀美\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 233.984px;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17);\">午餐：赠送风味路餐</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-style: dotted; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-title\" style=\"margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17);\">华阴&nbsp;&nbsp;西安</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-journey-seprate\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-style: dotted; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 18p