  </div>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0px 0px -1px; padding: 20px 0px 6px 100px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); zoom: 1; overflow: hidden;\">\r\n    <h5 class=\"time_list\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -100px; padding: 0px; float: left; display: inline; font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px; width: 80px; overflow: hidden;\">10：30</h5>\r\n    <div class=\"day_detail\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 30px; border-left: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204); position: relative; zoom: 1; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.5;\">\r\n    <p class=\"bg_important\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px 5px; line-height: 22px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); display: inline-block;\">游览时间: 约 4 小时</p>\r\n    <div class=\" day_scene_list border_none\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px; border-top: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204); border-right: 0px none !important; border-bottom: 0px none !important; border-left: 0px none !important; border-image: initial !important; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\">\r\n    <div class=\"scene_pic\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; float: right; display: inline;\"><a poiid=\"10558616\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p13784638s28.html?kwd=%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\"><img poiid=\"10558616\" title=\"海洋公园\" src=\"https://dimg06.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g2/M05/8A/25/CghzgFWwybGAPwdKAB7HoTuJ6yo155_C_210_118.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; width: 210px; height: 118px; vertical-align: top; cursor: pointer; opacity: 1;\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n    <h6 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\"><a poiid=\"10558616\" title=\"海洋公园\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p13784638s28.html?kwd=%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\">海洋公园</a></h6>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\">海洋公园是世界最大的水族馆之一，也是到香港必游的场所之一。</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">前往闻名世界的海洋公园（约 4 小时午餐园内自理），这里有世界最大的水族馆、鲨鱼馆及海洋剧场，有海豚、海狮、杀人鲸等精彩特技表演；还有各式各样惊险刺激的机动游乐设施，如过山车、摩天轮、海盗船等。游毕乘亚洲最长的户外登山电梯下行参观集古村 -- 置身其中，仿佛走进时光隧道，重温中国过去十三个朝代历史，场内有艺术品及工艺品制作示范、街头表演等。<br />\r\n    指定时间集中（温馨提示：由于时间有限，请游客严格按照导游的时间集合，否则追团的费用需要游客自理）</p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0px 0px -1px; padding: 20px 0px 6px 100px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); zoom: 1; overflow: hidden;\">\r\n    <h5 class=\"time_list\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -100px; padding: 0px; float: left; display: inline; font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px; width: 80px; overflow: hidden;\">14：30</h5>\r\n    <div class=\"day_detail\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 30px; border-left: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204); position: relative; zoom: 1; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.5;\">\r\n    <p class=\"bg_important\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px 5px; line-height: 22px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); display: inline-block;\">游览时间: 约 1 小时 30 分钟</p>\r\n    <div class=\" day_scene_list border_none\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px; border-top: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204); border-right: 0px none !important; border-bottom: 0px none !important; border-left: 0px none !important; border-image: initial !important; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\">\r\n    <div class=\"scene_pic\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; float: right; display: inline;\"><a poiid=\"76012\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p13784638s28.html?kwd=%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\"><img poiid=\"76012\" title=\"太平山顶\" src=\"https://dimg09.c-ctrip.com/images/100c04000000093iz6B20_C_210_118.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; width: 210px; height: 118px; vertical-align: top; cursor: pointer; opacity: 1;\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n    <h6 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\"><a poiid=\"76012\" title=\"太平山顶\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p13784638s28.html?kwd=%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\">太平山顶</a></h6>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\">太平山是香港的最高峰，亦名维多利亚山，曾是英国人宣示主权的地方。</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">后前往香港最 高点太平山（合计约 1.5 小时），是游客必到的旅游点，乘车抵达山顶，山顶一带更是官绅名流的官邸所在。在这里可以俯瞰维多利亚港的香港岛、九龙半岛两岸，古式古香的狮子亭和空旷怡人的山顶公园是很好观赏位置。</p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0px 0px -1px; padding: 20px 0px 6px 100px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); zoom: 1; overflow: hidden;\">\r\n    <h5 class=\"time_list\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -100px; padding: 0px; float: left; display: inline; font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px; width: 80px; overflow: hidden;\">16：00</h5>\r\n    <div class=\"day_detail\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 30px; border-left: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204); position: relative; zoom: 1; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.5;\">\r\n    <p class=\"bg_important\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px 5px; line-height: 22px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); display: inline-block;\">游览时间: 约 30 分钟</p>\r\n    <div class=\" day_scene_list border_none\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px; border-top: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204); border-right: 0px none !important; border-bottom: 0px none !important; border-left: 0px none !important; border-image: initial !important; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\">\r\n    <div class=\"scene_pic\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; float: right; display: inline;\"><a poiid=\"76014\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p13784638s28.html?kwd=%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\"><img poiid=\"76014\" title=\"浅水湾\" src=\"https://dimg03.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g4/M06/A4/A5/CggYHFX6dV2AQdLxAB_3yGs1jl4268_C_210_118.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; width: 210px; height: 118px; vertical-align: top; cursor: pointer; opacity: 1;\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n    <h6 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\"><a poiid=\"76014\" title=\"浅水湾\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p13784638s28.html?kwd=%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\">浅水湾</a></h6>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\">号称 &ldquo;天下第一湾&rdquo;，也有 &ldquo;东方夏威夷&rdquo; 之美誉，是香港最具代表性的沙滩。</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"day_scene_list\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1; border-top: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204);\">\r\n    <div class=\"scene_pic\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; float: right; display: inline;\"><a poiid=\"81945\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p13784638s28.html?kwd=%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\"><img poiid=\"81945\" title=\"金紫荆广场\" src=\"https://dimg01.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g1/M00/7C/0E/CghzfVWwyFKALwVGAB7RQX5MUsk336_C_210_118.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; width: 210px; height: 118px; vertical-align: top; cursor: pointer; opacity: 1;\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n    <h6 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\"><a poiid=\"81945\" title=\"金紫荆广场\" sight=\"true\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p13784638s28.html?kwd=%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\">金紫荆广场</a></h6>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\">金紫荆广场位于香港湾仔香港会议展览中心新翼人工岛上，三面被维港包围，在维港的中心位置，与对岸的尖沙咀对峙，是观景的好地方，也是内地游客到香港的必游之地。</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">游览结束, 下山后途经风景如画的香港风水宝地浅水湾. 这里是香港最 具代表性的美丽海湾，其秀丽景色使它成为港岛著名的高级住宅区之一。随后到达香港会展中心新翼和金紫荆广场参观（约 30 分钟），这里是香港回归祖国的见证，&ldquo;永远盛开的紫荆花&rdquo; 面朝维多利亚海港，寓意着香港永远繁荣昌盛</p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0px 0px -1px; padding: 20px 0px 6px 100px; list-style: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); zoom: 1; overflow: hidden;\">\r\n    <h5 class=\"time_list\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -100px; padding: 0px; float: left; display: inline; font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px; width: 80px; overflow: hidden;\">17：00</h5>\r\n    <div class=\"day_detail\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 30px; border-left: 1px dotted rgb(204, 204, 204); position: relative; zoom: 1; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.5;\">\r\n    <p class=\"bg_important\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px 5px; line-height: 22px; position: relative; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); display: inline-block;\">用餐时间: 约 45 分钟</p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">晚餐: 用餐：含香港本地酒楼晚餐 (参考餐厅富临酒楼)<br />\r\n    参考餐单 (此为参考菜单，以实际用餐为准)<br />\r\n    烧味拼盘 酱油鸡 蒸海上鲜 翡翠炒肉片 粟米羹 白灼时蔬 红烧豆腐 鱼香茄子煲 丝苗白饭</p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0px 0px -1px; paddin