Forte Orange Hotel Liuhe)\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p1895419s28.html?kwd=%e5%8f%b0%e6%b9%be###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\">福泰桔子商旅六合店 (Forte Orange Hotel Liuhe)</a>&nbsp;或&nbsp;<a hotelid=\"533943\" hotel=\"true\" title=\"高雄立多商旅(Best Hotel)\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p1895419s28.html?kwd=%e5%8f%b0%e6%b9%be###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\">高雄立多商旅 (Best Hotel)</a>&nbsp;或&nbsp;<a hotelid=\"1050305\" hotel=\"true\" title=\"高雄河堤时尚旅店-爱河馆(The Riverside Hotel Fashion)\" href=\"http://vacations.ctrip.com/grouptravel/p1895419s28.html?kwd=%e5%8f%b0%e6%b9%be###\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); text-decoration: none; outline: none;\">高雄河堤时尚旅店 - 爱河馆 (The Riverside Hotel Fashion)</a></p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">或入住中正 / 中央大饭店、晶晶大饭店、滟时尚 / 昭来大饭店。</p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"day_list\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 1px solid rgb(229, 229, 229); zoom: 1; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n<div class=\"day_title\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px 0px 120px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(229, 229, 229); background: rgb(247, 247, 247); overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\"><a id=\"route_day5\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 101, 187); outline: none; margin-top: -169px; position: absolute;\">&nbsp;</a></div>\r\n</div>', 'images/201612/thumb_img/70_thumb_G_1482190728152.jpg', 'images/201612/goods_img/70_G_1482190728192.jpg', 'images/201612/source_img/70_G_1482190728330.jpg', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '28', '1482190728', '100', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1482192741', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '', '0', '0', '', '', '0', '0', '', '0');
